Dialogue: 9,0:00:06.22,0:00:08.88,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Začiatok Tretieho galaktického impéria.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:08.88,0:00:12.99,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vtedy to bol ešte 71. rok pravého kalendára.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:13.52,0:00:16.36,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nie je to náhodou úplný okraj galaxie?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.62,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Asi hej.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:17.78,0:00:20.37,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Tamtá planéta je Zem?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.00,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Všetko sa to začalo na takej malej planéte?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:22.00,0:00:27.25,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dokonca ani nie na nej. Všetko to spôsobil jeden maličký modul.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:27.43,0:00:29.17,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Modul?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:29.17,0:00:31.76,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dnes už nikto nepoužíva také slovo, čo?
Dialogue: 9,0:00:32.13,0:00:35.38,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Prvý z nás, zakladateľ,
Dialogue: 9,0:00:35.38,0:00:40.28,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,stratil mnoho priateľov v boji o Modul 77.
Dialogue: 9,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.57,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,A to je zároveň aj miesto, kde prvýkrát stretol Mága.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:50.94,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com
Dialogue: 9,0:02:15.70,0:02:17.07,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Rukino Saki,
Dialogue: 9,0:02:18.04,0:02:18.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,vydala...
Dialogue: 9,0:02:19.85,0:02:20.95,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,by si sa za mňa?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:23.32,0:02:26.94,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Chcem k tomu pristúpiť zodpovedne.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:28.45,0:02:29.67,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ty si sa asi načisto zbláznil, však?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:29.67,0:02:30.54,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo?
Dialogue: 9,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Som idol, ak si si nevšimol.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.36,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem patriť jednej osobe.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.88,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ale po tom, čo som spravil—
Dialogue: 9,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Si ako malý, Haruto.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.52,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Som slávna!
Dialogue: 9,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.75,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Každý deň sa s týmto stretávam.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.96,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Pustil by si do gatí, kebyže ti poviem, aké veci sa odohrávajú vo svete dospelých.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.27,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ale ja viem, že ty taká nie—
Dialogue: 9,0:02:48.64,0:02:53.14,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Rovnako ako ja vieš, že máš v sebe posvätného ducha.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:54.24,0:02:57.69,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,A teraz choď a zachráň nášho premiéra.
Dialogue: 9,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.94,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Mám ju celkom rada.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.22,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vidíš, čo keby si prišla sem?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.06,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Odmietla som...
Dialogue: 9,0:03:36.06,0:03:39.12,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Odmietla som ju...
Dialogue: 9,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.10,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sashinami Shoko. Je čas ísť.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:45.40,0:03:48.37,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Alebo chceš, aby smrť tvojho otca vyšla navnivoč?
Dialogue: 9,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.88,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,L-Elf kde si?!
Dialogue: 9,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.16,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,V škole.
Dialogue: 9,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.51,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sashinami je tu so mnou.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:01.52,0:04:04.04,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Môj Valvrave je nepoužiteľný.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:04.04,0:04:07.39,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Použi mňa na vylákanie Dorssiánov z modulu.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.16,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Konečne ti to začína myslieť.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.68,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Počkaj ma na druhom ihrisku.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.39,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vyzdvihnem ťa.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:12.39,0:04:13.88,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.86,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,A povedz Shoko...
Dialogue: 9,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.63,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,...že vyhrám za každú cenu.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.49,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Počula si to?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.86,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nepovedz o tom Harutovi.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:24.02,0:04:28.34,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Pretože Tokishima Haruto by sa utrápil z faktu, že zabil tvojho otca?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.34,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vy dvaja ste si naozaj podobní.
Dialogue: 9,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.00,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Prerazili ochrannú bránu G-17!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.75,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vesmírny dok stráca energiu!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:38.75,0:04:42.00,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to tak, že votrelci aktivovali nejaké vŕtacie zariadenie!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.80,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,O 60 minút dorazí až ku škole!
Dialogue: 9,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.26,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To hádam nie! Ku škole?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.04,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To je skutočné vŕtacie zariadenie, však?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:54.04,0:04:55.65,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čiže sme vlastne v koncoch?
Dialogue: 9,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.02,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ide hore. Utečte!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:02.23,0:05:04.40,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo to?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.06,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Pália ma oči—
Dialogue: 9,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.41,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Yuuta?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:18.17,0:05:20.29,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Utekajte hore!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.86,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Tu nemôžeme zostať!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.30,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Jedovatý plyn?!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.20,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je to pravda?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.13,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Akonáhle sa dostane hore, tak otrávi vzduch v celom module
Dialogue: 9,0:05:29.13,0:05:32.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Akonáhle sa dostane hore, tak otrávi vzduch v celom module
Dialogue: 9,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.02,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,a my zomrieme!
Dialogue: 9,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.35,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Takže porušenie novoguinejskej dohody, čo?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.21,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nakoniec si použil všetky prostriedky, aby si dosiahol svoje, Cain.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:39.21,0:05:40.20,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Poznáš ho?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:40.20,0:05:43.46,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je to vojnový hrdina, ktorý získal najmenej tri medaily za odvahu.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:43.46,0:05:47.76,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Bol v centre diania pred dvanástimi rokmi a teraz je súčasťou smotánky.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:47.76,0:05:48.49,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Navyše...
Dialogue: 9,0:05:49.20,0:05:51.24,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,...ma naučil všetko, čo viem.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.50,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Si vojak, nie?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.64,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 9,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.70,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Tá jazva na tvojom pravom ramene je od strely.
Dialogue: 9,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.13,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Kaliber 45.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:02.13,0:06:06.92,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Podľa toho, ako zle je zahojená, usudzujem, že ťa ošetrili priamo na bojisku.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.39,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Takisto nemáš mozole na rukách, z čoho usudzujem, že si medik alebo vedec.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:10.59,0:06:14.89,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vypočujem ho osobitne. Daj ho na zoznam.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.14,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Kam idete, plukovník?
Dialogue: 9,0:06:18.07,0:06:19.48,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Musím stihnúť promócie.
Dialogue: 9,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.90,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Doktor?! Doktor!!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.10,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Jedovatý plyn?! Hlbšie ste už nemohli klesnúť!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.73,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Keď niečo nepodnikneme, tak všetci zomrú!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:32.73,0:06:35.15,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Musíme zastaviť ten vrták za každú cenu!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.91,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vráťme sa späť!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.80,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Budem tvoj štít. Yamada, kry ju!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.86,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ty by si mala viesť útok!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:46.86,0:06:47.68,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Rozumiem!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.88,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,"Thunder"!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.56,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Haru—
Dialogue: 9,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.57,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sashinami, si to ty?!
Dialogue: 9,0:06:58.57,0:07:00.23,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To som ja! Renboukouji!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.23,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Prosím, zachráň moju sestru! Zachráň Akiru!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:03.43,0:07:08.07,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ten vrták smeruje na školu! Akira je v smrteľnom nebezpečí!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.07,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Satomi...
Dialogue: 9,0:07:08.07,0:07:12.57,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Keď bola malá, šikanovali ju, a preto sa bojí vyjsť von.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.46,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nezdvíha mi telefón, ani nereaguje na správy.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.39,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Prosím ťa, Sashinami! Si jediná, na koho sa môžem—
Dialogue: 9,0:07:25.87,0:07:26.88,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemiešaj sa do toho!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:26.88,0:07:27.51,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Akira?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.67,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Akira?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.16,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nebojím sa.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.36,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Som tu, lebo sa mi tu páči.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.16,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nie sú tu zlí ľudia.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.08,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiotov to filtruje automaticky.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.60,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je tu spravodlivosť!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.93,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Svet, ktorý patrí iba mne!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.06,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nechať zaútočiť nepriateľov na stroj 1?
Dialogue: 9,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.68,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Bude to trójsky kôň.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:42.68,0:07:46.09,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Skryjeme sa v strojovni a potom ich napadneme.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.20,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je to príliš riskantné!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.29,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nie je čas na bezpečnejšie alternatívy.
Dialogue: 9,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.95,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Naším nepriateľom je Cain!
Dialogue: 9,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.44,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To hádam nie...
Dialogue: 9,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.21,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sledovali ho!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.09,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Cain!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:09.09,0:08:13.16,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vítam ťa, moje majstrovské dielo.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:13.16,0:08:16.48,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,A promócie sa môžu začať.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.73,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Úžasný Thunder vás zbaví toho prekliateho plynu!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.83,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Tím Piedra Del Sol, Valvrave sa vracajú späť!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:33.83,0:08:35.70,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,A-Drei je s plukovníkom.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.80,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To som už počula od plukovníka.
Dialogue: 9,0:08:37.80,0:08:41.25,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Hej, ľudia, hádajte kto je späť?!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.13,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Pre mňa ste iba malé mušky!
Dialogue: 9,0:08:56.88,0:09:00.64,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Tu máš! Pästný guľomet!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.77,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ako sa ti to páčilo?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.90,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Tie vaše triky na mňa neplatia!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.90,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo! Zohrieva sa!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:15.10,0:09:17.36,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Iba som udrel!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo, doriti?!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.85,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je to vôbec možné?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.22,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To si robíš zo mňa srandu!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.99,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Uviazol si, Yamada?!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:26.99,0:09:29.06,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Prekročil som 100 %!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.42,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Oni ho žehlia!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.26,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Idea je jednoduchá,
Dialogue: 9,0:09:35.50,0:09:39.89,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,ale plukovník si to všimol!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.14,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je to naozaj {\i1}horúci{\i0} nápad!
Dialogue: 9,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.64,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Takže trójsky kôň?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.15,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je to síce starý trik, ale nie zlý.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:48.36,0:09:50.66,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Zoberiem si tento stroj.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.53,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Pre budúcnosť nášho klanu.
Dialogue: 9,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.61,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ako sa len opovažuješ?!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:02.89,0:10:06.03,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nesmrteľnosť. Musí byť z tretej generácie.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.91,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Bez zaváhania by si zabil svojho učiteľa, čo?
Dialogue: 9,0:10:11.91,0:10:13.28,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Za to by si si zaslúžil najlepšiu známku S!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.00,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Avšak...
Dialogue: 9,0:10:15.06,0:10:17.29,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Isto vieš,
Dialogue: 9,0:10:17.29,0:10:19.97,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,že nado mnou nemôžeš vyhrať.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.60,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vrták dosiahol piatu úroveň!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.02,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Boh nás chráň!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:30.51,0:10:32.69,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Teplo sa prenáša aj cez štít?!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.74,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dochádza mi čas.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.41,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,V tom prípade...
Dialogue: 9,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.80,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nezáleží na tom, akú silnú máš ochranu.
Dialogue: 9,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.33,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je to zbytočné!
Dialogue: 9,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.96,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Piedra Del Sol je najlepší!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.24,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Inuzuka!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:21.72,0:11:23.91,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Tvoja obrana je slabá ako vždy.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:24.22,0:11:26.49,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Známka E.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.66,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemožné! Je silnejší ako ja!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.17,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Utekaj, L-Elf!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.92,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Iba ty nás dokážeš dostať z tejto situácie.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.93,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Uteč a poraz ho!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:40.93,0:11:43.29,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Už druhýkrát za dnešný deň máš pravdu!
Dialogue: 9,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.81,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vidím, že si si našiel priateľov.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:49.03,0:11:52.01,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ako starneme, tak sa priatelia stávajú cennejší.
Dialogue: 9,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.02,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Však, A-Drei?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:59.60,0:12:03.87,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Plukovník mi prikázal s tebou vyjednávať.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:03.87,0:12:08.08,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Neboj, keď bude po všetkom, tak si vezmem tvoje oko.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:09.29,0:12:14.36,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Budeš moje ľavé oko a spolu sa postavíme na čelo revolúcie.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.68,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nepriatelia sú tu!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.09,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Zomrieš, ak tu zostaneš!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.60,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A čo?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.63,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Radšej zomriem,
Dialogue: 9,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ako by som mala vyjsť von!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:21.84,0:12:25.18,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zmením sa na blchu!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.80,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nechcem viesť taký život!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.92,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ty už si blcha, Satomi!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.10,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Žiješ obklopená tými beštiami!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Radšej budem žiť sama
Dialogue: 9,0:12:31.84,0:12:33.06,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a sama aj zomriem!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.96,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Zbláznila si sa?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.57,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Zbláznila si sa?!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:39.64,0:12:42.98,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je ti jedno, že zomrieš?! Mne nie!
Dialogue: 9,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.78,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Takže sa ma nesmú dotknúť, čo?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.34,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Rozumiem!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.84,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ty malý parchant!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:02.02,0:13:05.09,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Skap. Nechám zovrieť tvoju krv.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:08.01,0:13:11.06,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Všetky jednotky sú imobilné.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.37,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To je zlé, nie?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.39,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Takahi?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.19,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Iori, kde je Tokishima?!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:15.46,0:13:17.77,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že s L-Elfom.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.54,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,"Myslíš"?!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.60,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Zavolaj ho, ihneď!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:21.60,0:13:22.15,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vykonám!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.19,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vrták sa dostal na úroveň 2!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:29.21,0:13:31.45,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Viem sa o seba postarať!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.25,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nechoď sem! Nechaj ma na pokoji!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.10,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Láska, smiech, slnko. Všetko bude preč!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.33,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Už nikdy viac sa nebudeme môcť stretnúť ani porozprávať!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.78,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Žiadna nenávisť ani násilie!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.59,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Si rovnaká ako oni!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:49.59,0:13:51.64,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Budeš sa mi vysmievať a ľutovať ma.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.39,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vravíš, že mám ísť von a potom sa na mňa nahneváš.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.22,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ja už som naštvaná!
Dialogue: 9,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.44,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vidíš?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.94,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Pretože sme priatelia!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:01.83,0:14:04.22,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy sme ... neboli priatelia!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:04.22,0:14:04.92,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.22,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,No už sme!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.93,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemôžeš o tom rozhodnúť za mňa!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.70,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, už som!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.20,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Si sebecká!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.18,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Neber priateľstvo na ľahkú váhu!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:21.72,0:14:24.71,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sme predsa priatelia, nie?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.34,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 9,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.89,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vrták dosiahol úroveň 1!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.35,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je po nás!
Dialogue: 9,0:14:48.47,0:14:50.95,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dokelu... čo spravím?
Dialogue: 9,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.47,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo mám robiť?
Dialogue: 9,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.44,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dovoľte, aby sme vám umyli chrbát, milostivá pani!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.46,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ste špinavá.
Dialogue: 9,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.00,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Máš pekné vlasy!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.88,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Krátky strih ti sekne!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.09,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Presne sa hodí tvojej divokej povahe!
Dialogue: 9,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.63,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nemôžem...
Dialogue: 9,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.60,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sľúbila som jej,
Dialogue: 9,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.99,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}že spolu pôjdeme nakupovať!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.99,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Supermarket!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.55,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Som vonku!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.26,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Shoko! Shoko!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.22,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.31,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:38.31,0:16:39.22,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sho—
Dialogue: 9,0:16:42.24,0:16:45.06,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Shoko! Shoko!
Dialogue: 9,0:16:49.87,0:16:52.58,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.44,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Už aj tak...
Dialogue: 9,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.87,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Shoko! Hej, Shoko!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.43,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Je nažive!
Dialogue: 9,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.64,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nezastaví sa!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.64,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To je čo?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.15,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Moja zbraň...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.15,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo sa deje?!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.83,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Hacker?!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:35.69,0:18:36.76,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo to?!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.33,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Stroj 6?
Dialogue: 9,0:18:41.33,0:18:42.51,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Kto ho riadi?!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.77,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,H-Neun, pošli naň Waffe!
Dialogue: 9,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.64,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Zmiznite...
Dialogue: 9,0:18:48.64,0:18:51.56,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,...preč!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:03.47,0:19:05.49,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,H-Neun! Čo to stváraš?!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.75,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ja nič! Tie stroje si robia, čo sa im zapáči!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.63,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dokelu!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.59,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Zastreľ ho, Haruto!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.73,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Veď je neozbrojený!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.15,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Urob to, je príliš nebezpečný!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:42.44,0:19:45.50,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ochránim našu krajinu!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:45.50,0:19:48.33,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Povedali sme, že sa nevzdáme!
Dialogue: 9,0:19:49.83,0:19:53.33,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Cain, akokoľvek môžeš byť silný, ale toto nemôžeš prežiť!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.01,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Netrafil som ho?!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.10,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Nemožné!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:08.28,0:20:13.14,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Povedal som ti. Nemôžeš nado mnou víťaziť.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:20.64,0:20:22.07,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,To hádam nie?!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:22.27,0:20:25.07,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čo si zač?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.44,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Vyhral som, Cain, ten stroj je nefunkčný.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:56.16,0:20:59.36,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Viem, že máš v sebe iba zlé spomienky,
Dialogue: 9,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.18,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,ale spolieham sa na teba, Blue.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.20,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Prekliati ľudia!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:09.98,0:21:10.95,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Čože?!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.95,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,B— Br—
Dialogue: 9,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.29,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Ona rozpráva?!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:14.48,0:21:18.29,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Bra— Braček!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.80,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Má ľudskú formu?!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:42.09,0:21:44.25,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Stroj číslo dva bol nefunkčný.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:44.25,0:21:47.96,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Iba študenti, špeciálne na to určení, môžu pilotovať Valvrave.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.09,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Dokázal sa chopiť svetla Valvrave bez akéhokoľvek špeciálneho vybavenia.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:51.09,0:21:54.79,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Všetko nasvedčuje tomu, že nie je človek!
Dialogue: 9,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.79,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo{\i0} si Cain?!
Dialogue: 9,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.82,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Sme Mágovia.
Dialogue: 9,0:22:27.58,0:22:30.52,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Riadime svet spoza tieňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:37.66,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Preklad a časovanie: \NKuro-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:40.66,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Korekcia:\NHaany
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.66,0:22:44.66,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com\N2015
Dialogue: 9,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.20,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Zomriem?
Dialogue: 9,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.46,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vyber ďalšieho pilota.
Dialogue: 9,0:23:57.46,0:23:59.20,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Bojíš sa o mňa?
Dialogue: 9,0:23:59.20,0:24:00.60,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Zachráň ma, Haruto!
Dialogue: 9,0:24:00.60,0:24:01.37,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}L-Elf!
Dialogue: 9,0:24:01.37,0:24:01.87,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ty hajzel!
Dialogue: 9,0:24:01.87,0:24:04.79,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tokishima Haruto navrhol seba za pokusného králika.
Dialogue: 9,0:24:04.79,0:24:07.34,Valvrave,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Táto kliatba zomrie spolu so mnou!
